INSERT INTO `articles` VALUES ('20150624033012', 'nb953.jpg', '10 Pleasant Smells That Can Change Your Mood And Productivity', 'Aromatherapy\r\nprobably\r\nisn''t the\r\nfirst tool\r\nyou think\r\nof to help\r\nboost your\r\nproductivity\r\nand grow\r\nyour\r\nbusiness,\r\nbut maybe\r\nit should\r\nbe. Smell\r\nis the\r\nstrongest\r\nof the\r\nsenses and\r\nis best\r\nable to\r\ninfluence\r\nbrain\r\nactivity.\r\nOlfactory\r\nbulbs are\r\npart of\r\nthe limbic\r\nsystem and\r\ndirectly\r\nconnect to\r\nthe areas\r\nof the\r\nbrain that\r\nprocess\r\nemotion\r\nand\r\nlearning.\r\n"This is\r\none of the\r\nreasons\r\nwhy so\r\noften\r\nsomething\r\nthat we\r\nsmell will\r\ntrigger a\r\nmemory or\r\nremind us\r\nof\r\nsomething\r\nor\r\nsomeone,"\r\nsays\r\nBeverley\r\nHawkins,\r\nowner of\r\nthe\r\nVancouver-based\r\nWest Coast\r\nInstitute\r\nof\r\nAromatherapy.\r\nEssential\r\noils not\r\nonly help\r\nimprove\r\njob\r\nperformance but\r\nhealth,\r\nmeaning\r\nemployees\r\nare less\r\nlikely to\r\ntake sick\r\ntime.\r\n"Essential\r\noils\r\nhave\r\nanti-viral, anti-bacterial\r\nand\r\nanti-fungal properties\r\nand using\r\nthem in an\r\nenvironment where\r\nthere are\r\na lot of\r\npeople can\r\nhelp to\r\nkeep germs\r\nat bay,"\r\nsays\r\nHawkins.\r\nInhaling\r\nessential\r\noils\r\nactivates\r\nthe\r\nhypothalamus\r\nâ€“ the area\r\nof the\r\nbrain\r\nwhich\r\nsends\r\nmessages\r\nto other\r\nparts of\r\nthe body.\r\n"A simple\r\ninhalation\r\nof an\r\naroma can\r\ncause many\r\nchanges in\r\nthe\r\nbody,"\r\nsays\r\nHawkins,\r\nincluding\r\nactivating\r\nthe immune\r\nsystem,\r\naffecting\r\nblood\r\npressure\r\nand\r\nstimulating digestion.\r\nHere are\r\nten scents\r\nthat\r\nHawkins\r\nrecommends\r\nfor\r\nboosting\r\nyour\r\nproductivity,\r\nmood and\r\nmore at\r\nwork:\r\n<br>\r\n1.\r\nVanilla:- \r\nVanilla\r\nmay often\r\nbe used as\r\na synonym\r\nfor\r\n"bland,"\r\nbut this\r\nscent is\r\nanything\r\nthat comes\r\nto our\r\nhappiness\r\nlevels. In\r\na study\r\npublished\r\nin the\r\nProceedings of\r\nISOT/JASTS\r\n2004,\r\nresearchers found\r\nthat\r\ntaking a\r\nwhiff of\r\nvanilla\r\nbean\r\nelevated\r\nparticipants''\r\nfeelings\r\nof joy and\r\nrelaxation. The\r\nresults\r\nwere\r\nmeasured\r\nthrough\r\nmood\r\nmapping,\r\nwhich\r\nincluded\r\nemotions\r\nranging\r\nfrom\r\nhappiness\r\nand\r\nstimulation to\r\napathy and\r\nirritation. \r\n<br> <a\r\nhref="http://www.fab8thproductions.com/pictures/Vanilla.jpg"\r\ntarget="_blank">\r\n<img\r\nsrc="http://www.fab8thproductions.com/pictures/Vanilla.jpg"\r\nwidth="400" height="220"/>\r\n</a> <br>\r\n \r\n\r\n2. Lemon:-\r\n <br>This\r\nscent\r\npromotes\r\nconcentration\r\nand has\r\ncalming\r\nand\r\nclarifying\r\nproperties\r\nthat are\r\nhelpful\r\nwhen\r\nyou''re\r\nfeeling\r\nangry,\r\nanxious or\r\nrun down.\r\nLemon also\r\nhas\r\nantiviral\r\nand\r\nantibacterial\r\nproperties\r\nand can\r\nhelp fight\r\nsore\r\nthroats\r\nand colds\r\nby\r\nboosting\r\nthe\r\nbody''s\r\nimmune\r\nsystem and\r\nimproving\r\ncirculation \r\n <br> <a\r\nhref="http://www.fab8thproductions.com/pictures/lemon2.jpg"\r\ntarget="_blank">\r\n<img\r\nsrc="http://www.fab8thproductions.com/pictures/lemon2.jpg"\r\nwidth="400" height="220"/>\r\n</a> <br>\r\n \r\n3.\r\nLavender:-\r\n<br> This\r\nessential\r\noil has\r\ncalming\r\nproperties\r\nthat help\r\ncontrol\r\nemotional\r\nstress.\r\nLavender\r\nhas a\r\nsoothing\r\neffect on\r\nnerves and\r\ncan\r\nrelieve\r\nnervous\r\ntension\r\nand\r\ndepression\r\nas well as\r\ntreat\r\nheadaches\r\nand\r\nmigraines\r\n <br> <a\r\nhref="http://www.fab8thproductions.com/pictures/lavender1.jpg"\r\ntarget="_blank">\r\n<img\r\nsrc="http://www.fab8thproductions.com/pictures/lavender1.jpg"\r\nwidth="400" height="220"/>\r\n</a> <br>\r\n \r\n\r\n4.\r\nJasmine:-\r\n  <br>\r\nLike\r\nlavender,\r\njasmine it\r\nis also\r\nused to\r\ncalm\r\nnerves,\r\nbut this\r\noil is\r\nalso\r\ncommonly\r\nused as an\r\nanti-depressant\r\nbecause of\r\nits\r\nuplifting\r\ncapabilities\r\nthat\r\nproduce a\r\nfeeling of\r\nconfidence, optimism\r\nand\r\nrevitalized energy\r\n <br> <a\r\nhref="http://www.fab8thproductions.com/pictures/jasmine\r\n\r\noil.jpg"\r\ntarget="_blank">\r\n<img\r\nsrc="http://www.fab8thproductions.com/pictures/jasmine\r\n oil.jpg"\r\nwidth="400" height="220"/>\r\n</a> <br>\r\n  \r\n\r\n5.\r\nRosemary:-\r\n<br> This\r\nis the\r\nperfect\r\nMonday\r\nmorning\r\npick-me-up. In\r\naddition\r\nto\r\nimproving\r\nmemory\r\nretention,\r\nrosemary\r\nhas\r\nstimulating properties\r\nthat fight\r\nphysical\r\nexhaustion, headaches\r\nand mental\r\nfatigue.\r\n"It''s\r\nexcellent\r\nto use in\r\nthe\r\nmornings\r\nwhen one\r\nneeds a\r\nbit of\r\nhelp\r\ngetting\r\ngoing,"\r\nsays\r\nHawkins.\r\nRosemary\r\ncan also\r\nbe used\r\ntopically\r\nto relieve\r\nmuscular\r\naches and\r\npains.  \r\n<br> <a\r\nhref="http://www.fab8thproductions.com/pictures/rosemary.jpg"\r\ntarget="_blank">\r\n<img\r\nsrc="http://www.fab8thproductions.com/pictures/rosemary.jpg"\r\nwidth="400" height="220"/>\r\n</a> <br>\r\n <br> \r\n\r\n6.\r\nCinnamon:-\r\n<br> The\r\nstimulating properties\r\nin\r\ncinnamon\r\ncan help\r\nfight\r\nmental\r\nfatigue\r\nand\r\nimprove\r\nconcentration\r\nand focus.\r\n  \r\n <br> <a\r\nhref="http://www.fab8thproductions.com/pictures/cinnamon.jpg"\r\ntarget="_blank">\r\n<img\r\nsrc="http://www.fab8thproductions.com/pictures/cinnamon.jpg"\r\nwidth="400" height="220"/>\r\n</a> <br> \r\n\r\n\r\n7.\r\nPeppermint:-\r\nTry\r\npeppermint\r\nwhen\r\nbrainstorming.\r\nAn energy\r\nbooster,\r\nthis scent\r\ninvigorates the\r\nmind,\r\npromotes\r\nconcentration\r\nand\r\nstimulates\r\nclear\r\nthinking.\r\n  <br> <a\r\nhref="http://www.fab8thproductions.com/pictures/Peppermint.jpg"\r\ntarget="_blank">\r\n<img\r\nsrc="http://www.fab8thproductions.com/pictures/Peppermint.jpg"\r\nwidth="400" height="220"/>\r\n</a> <br>\r\n \r\n\r\n8.\r\nApples:- \r\nYou know\r\nwhat they\r\nsay, "an\r\napple a\r\nday keeps\r\nthe doctor\r\naway" --\r\nand that\r\nmay be\r\nmore true\r\nwhen it\r\ncomes to\r\nheadaches.\r\nResearch\r\nhas\r\nsuggested\r\nthat the\r\nsmell of\r\nthe crisp\r\nfruit may\r\nactually\r\nhelp ease\r\na\r\nmigraine.\r\nOne 2008\r\nstudy\r\nshowed\r\nthat those\r\nwho found\r\nthe scent\r\nappealing\r\nhad a\r\nnoticeable\r\nreduction\r\nin\r\nheadache\r\nsymptoms\r\nas well as\r\nshortened\r\nmigraine\r\nepisodes.\r\nPrevious\r\nstudies on\r\na green\r\napple''s\r\nodor have\r\nalso found\r\nthe scent\r\nmay help\r\ncontrol\r\nfeelings\r\nof anxiety\r\nduring\r\nstressful\r\nmoments. \r\n <br> <a\r\nhref="http://www.fab8thproductions.com/pictures/Apples.jpg"\r\ntarget="_blank">\r\n<img\r\nsrc="http://www.fab8thproductions.com/pictures/Apples.jpg"\r\nwidth="400" height="220"/>\r\n</a> <br>\r\n \r\n9. Olive\r\noil:- \r\nWe''ve all\r\nheard the\r\nbenefits\r\nof using\r\nolive oil\r\nin our\r\ndishes (it\r\ncan reduce\r\nyour\r\nchances of\r\ngetting a\r\nstroke and\r\nis heart\r\nhealthy\r\nfor\r\nstarters),\r\nbut the\r\nkey\r\ningredient\r\nin your\r\nMediterranean\r\ndiet may\r\nalso help\r\ncurb\r\ncravings\r\njust by\r\nsmelling\r\nit.\r\nResearch\r\nout of the\r\nGerman\r\nResearch\r\nCenter for\r\nFood\r\nChemistry\r\nfound that\r\nolive oil\r\nwas more\r\nlikely to\r\nmake a\r\nperson\r\nfeel\r\nsatisfied\r\nafter a\r\nmeal\r\ncompared\r\nto other\r\noils and\r\nfats.\r\nFurthermore,\r\nthe study\r\nalso found\r\nthat just\r\nby having\r\nthe scent\r\nof olive\r\noil\r\nassociated\r\nwith the\r\nfood\r\nreduced\r\nthe total\r\namount of\r\ncalories\r\nparticipants\r\nconsumed.\r\n <br> <a\r\nhref="http://www.fab8thproductions.com/pictures/Oliveoil.jpg"\r\ntarget="_blank">\r\n<img\r\nsrc="http://www.fab8thproductions.com/pictures/Oliveoil.jpg"\r\nwidth="400" height="220"/>\r\n</a> <br>\r\n \r\n\r\n10.\r\nPumpkin:- \r\nWould you\r\never\r\nconsider a\r\nlittle Eau\r\nde\r\nPumpkin?\r\nIt might\r\nbe an\r\nalluring\r\nscent for\r\nmen. In a\r\nstudy\r\nconducted\r\nby The\r\nSmell &\r\nTaste\r\nTreatment\r\nand\r\nResearch\r\nFoundation, researchers\r\ndiscovered\r\nthat 40\r\npercent of\r\nthe male\r\ntest\r\nsubjects\r\nresponded\r\npositively\r\nto a\r\npumpkin\r\nscent when\r\ncombined\r\nwith\r\nlavender.\r\n<br> It\r\nalso serve\r\nas an\r\naphrodisiac.\r\n<br> <a\r\nhref="http://www.fab8thproductions.com/pictures/Pumpkin.jpg"\r\ntarget="_blank">\r\n<img\r\nsrc="http://www.fab8thproductions.com/pictures/Pumpkin.jpg"\r\nwidth="400" height="220"/>\r\n</a> <br>\r\n', '24-Jun-2015', '03:30 AM', 46);
INSERT INTO `articles` VALUES ('20150624231631', 'Tina Leggio.jpg', 'In Need Of\r\nMore Human\r\nFriends?\r\nThen See\r\nReasons\r\nWhy You\r\nNeed To\r\nGet A\r\nDog!', 'Dogs can\r\nserve as\r\nan\r\nicebreaker\r\nthat lets\r\nneighbors\r\nmeet and\r\nbecome\r\nfriends.\r\n<br> \r\nIt was a\r\nwarm\r\nspring\r\nday. I was\r\nout\r\nwalking my\r\nCavalier\r\nKing\r\nCharles\r\nSpaniel,\r\nRipley,\r\nwhen I ran\r\ninto a\r\nwoman from\r\nour\r\nneighborhood\r\nwho was\r\nwalking\r\nher little\r\nItalian\r\nGreyhound.\r\nIt was\r\nbecause we\r\nboth walk\r\nour dogs\r\nthat Nancy\r\nand I met\r\na year or\r\ntwo\r\nearlier.\r\nSince that\r\ntime I had\r\na chance\r\nto meet\r\nher\r\nhusband\r\nand her\r\ndaughter\r\nand I\r\nconsider\r\nthem all\r\nto be\r\nfriends.\r\nShe was\r\nquite\r\nexcited\r\nthis\r\nmorning\r\nand told\r\nme that a\r\ngroup of\r\nneighbors\r\nwas\r\ngetting\r\ntogether\r\nto talk\r\nabout some\r\nproposed\r\nrestrictive changes\r\nin parking\r\nregulations in\r\nour\r\nneighborhood\r\nthat she\r\nthought\r\nwould\r\nreduce the\r\nquality of\r\nlife for\r\nus. I\r\nlistened\r\ncarefully\r\nand agreed\r\nto join\r\nthe group\r\nto get a\r\nbit more\r\ninformation.\r\n  As we\r\nparted\r\nthat\r\nmorning I\r\nhad the\r\nfeeling\r\nthat I had\r\nspoken\r\nwith a\r\nfriend and\r\nI was part\r\nof a\r\nwelcoming\r\nand\r\nsupportive\r\ncommunity\r\nin my\r\nneighborhood\r\nâ€” all\r\nbecause of\r\ninformal\r\nencounters\r\nwith\r\npeople\r\nthat I\r\nmeet while\r\nwalking my\r\ndog. As it\r\nturns out,\r\nrecent\r\nscientific\r\ndata\r\nsuggests\r\nthat this\r\nis quite a\r\ncommon\r\nevent,\r\nwith dogs\r\nplaying a\r\nconstructive\r\nrole in\r\nbuilding\r\nsocial\r\nrelationships\r\n<br>\r\n\r\n <br><br>\r\n<a\r\nhref="http://www.fab8thproductions.com/pictures/d.jpg"\r\ntarget="_blank">\r\n<img\r\nsrc="http://www.fab8thproductions.com/pictures/d.jpg"\r\nwidth="80%" height="280"/>\r\n</a>\r\n<br><br>\r\n\r\n <br><br>\r\n<a\r\nhref="http://www.fab8thproductions.com/pictures/dd.jpg"\r\ntarget="_blank">\r\n<img\r\nsrc="http://www.fab8thproductions.com/pictures/dd.jpg"\r\nwidth="80%" height="280"/>\r\n</a>\r\n<br><br>	\r\n\r\nIt is\r\nquite well\r\naccepted\r\nby now\r\nthat for\r\nan\r\nindividual\r\ndog\r\nownership\r\nhas a\r\npositive\r\neffect on\r\nhealth and\r\npsychological\r\nwell-being\r\n(click\r\nhere or\r\nhere or\r\nhere for\r\nexamples).\r\nFor people\r\nwho are\r\ndealing\r\nwith\r\nloneliness\r\nand\r\nstress,\r\ndogs can\r\nbe a vital\r\nsource of\r\nboth\r\nemotional\r\nand social\r\nsupport\r\n(for an\r\nexample\r\nclick\r\nhere).\r\nHowever\r\nthe idea\r\nthat dogs\r\ncan also\r\nserve as a\r\nmeans of\r\ndeveloping\r\nfriends\r\nand social\r\ncontacts\r\nis only\r\nnow\r\nreceiving\r\nsome\r\ndirect\r\nexperimental\r\ntesting.\r\n<br>According\r\nto\r\nFab8thproductions.com,\r\nthe most\r\nrecent\r\nresearch\r\non this\r\ntopic was\r\nconducted\r\nby a team\r\nof\r\ninvestigators\r\nheaded by\r\nLisa Wood,\r\nwho is at\r\nthe School\r\nof\r\nPopulation\r\nHealth at\r\nthe\r\nUniversity\r\nof Western\r\nAustralia.\r\nThe\r\nexperimental\r\nresults\r\nwere\r\npublished\r\nin the\r\njournal\r\nPLOS One*.\r\n\r\n<br><br>\r\n<a\r\nhref="http://www.fab8thproductions.com/pictures/ddd.jpg"\r\ntarget="_blank">\r\n<img\r\nsrc="http://www.fab8thproductions.com/pictures/ddd.jpg"\r\nwidth="80%" height="280"/>\r\n</a>\r\n<br><br>\r\n\r\n<br><br>\r\n<a\r\nhref="http://www.fab8thproductions.com/pictures/dddd.jpg"\r\ntarget="_blank">\r\n<img\r\nsrc="http://www.fab8thproductions.com/pictures/dddd.jpg"\r\nwidth="80%" height="280"/>\r\n</a>\r\n<br><br>\r\n\r\n\r\nThis was a\r\nlarge\r\nstudy\r\ninvolving\r\n2692\r\npeople who\r\nresponded\r\nto a\r\nrather\r\nextensive\r\ncomputer\r\nassisted\r\ntelephone\r\nsurvey.\r\nThe study\r\ninvolved\r\nfour\r\ncities,\r\nPerth in\r\nAustralia,\r\nand three\r\nUS cities:\r\nSan Diego,\r\nCalifornia; Portland,\r\nOregon and\r\nNashville,\r\nTennessee.\r\nThe\r\npurpose of\r\nthe\r\nresearch\r\nwas to see\r\nif pets\r\nplayed a\r\nrole in\r\npeople\r\ngetting to\r\nknow their\r\nneighborhood\r\nand\r\nforming\r\nfriendships.\r\nThe\r\nresults of\r\nthis\r\ninvestigation\r\nwere\r\nunambiguous.\r\nThe\r\nresearchers report\r\nthat "pet\r\nowners\r\nwere\r\nsignificantly\r\nmore\r\nlikely to\r\nget to\r\nknow\r\npeople in\r\ntheir\r\nneighborhood\r\nwhom they\r\ndidn''t\r\nknow\r\npreviously, compared\r\nwith\r\nnon-pet\r\nowners".\r\nAlthough\r\nthis study\r\nlooked at\r\nall forms\r\nof pet\r\nownership\r\n(including\r\ncats,\r\nrabbits,\r\nbirds\r\netc.)\r\nthese\r\ninvestigators\r\nfound that\r\ndog owners\r\nwere more\r\nlikely\r\nthan other\r\npet owners\r\nto report\r\nthat they\r\nhad got to\r\nknow\r\npeople in\r\nthe\r\nneighborhood\r\nthrough\r\ntheir pet.\r\nSpecifically,\r\ndog owners\r\nwere five\r\ntimes more\r\nlikely to\r\nget to\r\nknow\r\npeople in\r\ntheir\r\ncommunity\r\nthen other\r\npet\r\nowners.\r\nThe\r\nmechanism\r\nfor this\r\nseems to\r\ninvolve\r\nthe\r\nprocess of\r\nwalking\r\nthe dog,\r\nsince when\r\nthe dog\r\nowners\r\nwere\r\nseparated\r\nby whether\r\nthey\r\nregularly\r\nwalk their\r\ndog or do\r\nnot it was\r\nthose who\r\nwere\r\nregular\r\ndog\r\nwalkers\r\nthat were\r\nthe most\r\nlikely to\r\nget to\r\nknow\r\npeople in\r\ntheir\r\nlocality.\r\nHow this\r\nworks was\r\nillustrated by\r\nthe\r\ncomments\r\nof some of\r\nthe people\r\nparticipating\r\nin the\r\nstudy.<br>\r\n\r\n<br><br>\r\n<a\r\nhref="http://www.fab8thproductions.com/pictures/ddddd.jpg"\r\ntarget="_blank">\r\n<img\r\nsrc="http://www.fab8thproductions.com/pictures/ddddd.jpg"\r\nwidth="80%" height="280"/>\r\n</a>\r\n<br><br>\r\n\r\n<br><br>\r\n<a\r\nhref="http://www.fab8thproductions.com/pictures/dddddd.jpg"\r\ntarget="_blank">\r\n<img\r\nsrc="http://www.fab8thproductions.com/pictures/dddddd.jpg"\r\nwidth="80%" height="280"/>\r\n</a>\r\n<br><br>\r\n\r\n<br><br>\r\n<a\r\nhref="http://www.fab8thproductions.com/pictures/ddddddd.jpg"\r\ntarget="_blank">\r\n<img\r\nsrc="http://www.fab8thproductions.com/pictures/ddddddd.jpg"\r\nwidth="80%" height="280"/>\r\n</a>\r\n<br><br>\r\n\r\nA man from\r\nPerth\r\nsaid,\r\n"People\r\nalways\r\nstop,\r\ncomplete\r\nstrangers\r\nwill stop,\r\nand talk\r\nto you\r\nabout your\r\ndog and\r\nask you\r\nabout it.\r\nIt''s funny\r\nbut it\r\nseems to\r\nbe an\r\nicebreaker..."\r\n\r\nA man from\r\nPortland\r\nsaid,\r\n"Lots of\r\nfolks in\r\nthis\r\nneighborhood\r\nown and\r\nwalk dogs.\r\nThe dogs\r\ninsist on\r\nmeeting\r\nand\r\ngreeting,\r\nand their\r\nhumans\r\nfollow\r\nsuit. It\r\nhas caused\r\nme to be\r\nmore\r\nsocial\r\nthan is my\r\ninclination."\r\n\r\nA woman\r\nfrom San\r\nDiego\r\nsaid,\r\n"There is\r\na path in\r\nour\r\nneighborhood\r\nthat\r\npeople\r\nwalk along\r\nwith their\r\ndogs. When\r\nyou walk\r\nthat path\r\nat the\r\nsame time\r\nevery day\r\nyou run\r\ninto the\r\nsame\r\npeople and\r\nstart\r\nconversations\r\nand make\r\nfriends."\r\n\r\nIt appears\r\nthat dogs\r\nserve as\r\nwhat\r\npsychologists\r\ncall a\r\n"social\r\nlubricant." Asking\r\nor\r\ncommenting\r\nabout a\r\nperson''s\r\ndog is a\r\nsafe way\r\nof opening\r\na\r\nconversation,\r\nand most\r\npeople\r\ntend to\r\nfind it to\r\nbe a\r\npositive\r\nexperience, much\r\nlike the\r\nway that\r\nparents\r\nenjoy it\r\nwhen\r\nfavorable\r\nattention\r\nis paid to\r\ntheir\r\nchildren.\r\nThe dog\r\n"opens the\r\ndoor" and\r\ntwo\r\nstrangers\r\ncan choose\r\nto step\r\nthrough it\r\nand in the\r\nprocess\r\nbecome\r\nfriends.<br>\r\n\r\n<br><br>\r\n<a\r\nhref="http://www.fab8thproductions.com/pictures/dddddddd.jpg"\r\ntarget="_blank">\r\n<img\r\nsrc="http://www.fab8thproductions.com/pictures/dddddddd.jpg"\r\nwidth="80%" height="280"/>\r\n</a>\r\n<br><br>\r\n\r\n<br><br>\r\n<a\r\nhref="http://www.fab8thproductions.com/pictures/ddddddddd.jpg"\r\ntarget="_blank">\r\n<img\r\nsrc="http://www.fab8thproductions.com/pictures/ddddddddd.jpg"\r\nwidth="80%" height="280"/>\r\n</a>\r\n<br><br>\r\n\r\nMany\r\nfriendships begin\r\nbecause of\r\nencounters\r\nthat\r\nhappen\r\nwhile\r\npeople are\r\nwalking\r\ntheir dog.\r\nThese\r\nfriendly\r\nassociations\r\ncan become\r\nquite\r\nstrong and\r\ncan\r\nprovide a\r\nlot of\r\nsocial\r\nsupport.\r\nThis\r\nsupport\r\ncan take\r\nmany\r\ndifferent\r\nshapes\r\nsuch as\r\ntalking\r\nabout\r\nthings\r\nthat worry\r\nyou\r\n(emotional\r\nsupport),\r\ngetting\r\nuseful\r\ninformation about\r\nthe\r\nneighborhood\r\nor\r\nresources\r\n(informational\r\nsupport),\r\ngetting\r\nadvice\r\n(appraisal\r\nsupport),\r\nor\r\nreceiving\r\na favor\r\nsuch as\r\nhaving\r\nsomeone\r\ncollect\r\nyour mail\r\nwhen you\r\nare away\r\nor giving\r\nyou a ride\r\n(instrumental\r\nsupport).\r\nIn this\r\nstudy it\r\nwas found\r\nthat 42%\r\nof pet\r\nowners\r\nreceived\r\none or\r\nmore types\r\nof social\r\nsupport\r\nfrom\r\npeople\r\nthey first\r\ngot to\r\nknow\r\nthrough\r\ntheir pet.\r\nThese are\r\nexactly\r\nthe kinds\r\nof\r\nsupports\r\nthat\r\npsychologists\r\nsay\r\nimprove\r\nthe\r\nquality of\r\nlife for\r\npeople and\r\nreduce a\r\nperson''s\r\noverall\r\nstress\r\nlevel.\r\n\r\nBecause of\r\nthese\r\nfindings\r\nthe\r\nresearchers end\r\ntheir\r\npaper with\r\nan\r\nobservation and\r\nan implied\r\nrecommendation,\r\nspecifically,\r\n"Given\r\nfriendship\r\nnetworks\r\nand social\r\nsupport\r\nare\r\nassociated\r\nwith\r\nmental\r\nhealth and\r\nwell-being\r\nof\r\ncommunities;\r\nsupporting\r\npet\r\nownership\r\nmay well\r\nbe an\r\nunder-recognized\r\nconduit\r\nfor\r\nindividual\r\nand\r\ncommunity\r\nwellbeing." In\r\nsimple\r\nterms they\r\nare saying\r\nthat if we\r\nwant more\r\nfriendly\r\nneighborhoods\r\nand\r\ncommunities we\r\nshould\r\nsupport\r\npet\r\nownership\r\nand get\r\nthe dog\r\nowners out\r\nof the\r\nhouse and\r\nwalking\r\ntheir\r\ndogs.<br>\r\n\r\nSo trust\r\nus peeps\r\nwhenever\r\nyou are in\r\nneed of a\r\ntrue,\r\nhonest and\r\nreliable\r\nfriend; A\r\nDOG is\r\nwhat you\r\nneed.\r\n', '24-Jun-2015', '11:16 PM', 16);
INSERT INTO `articles` VALUES ('20150624235832', 'nn.jpg', ' Why Nosy\r\nPeople Ask\r\nNosy\r\nQuestions\r\nAnd 9 Ways\r\nTo Handle\r\nThem\r\n', 'Nosy\r\nquestions.\r\nWe all\r\nface them\r\nat least\r\nonce in a\r\nwhile. It\r\nmay be in\r\nthe\r\nprocess of\r\nmaking\r\nsmall talk\r\nwith\r\npeople we\r\ndonâ€™t know\r\nvery well.\r\nYou find\r\nyourself\r\ninadvertently\r\nbumping up\r\nagainst a\r\ntopic\r\nyouâ€™d\r\nrather not\r\ndiscuss.\r\nIt could\r\nbe a\r\nquestion\r\nas simple\r\nas the\r\nreason\r\nyour name\r\ndoesnâ€™t\r\nmatch that\r\nof your\r\npartner,\r\nchildren,\r\nor\r\nparents:\r\nâ€œOh, were\r\nyou\r\nmarried\r\nbefore?â€\r\nâ€œWhat was\r\nyour\r\nfamilyâ€™s\r\nname\r\nbefore\r\nyour\r\nfather\r\nchanged\r\nit?â€ Or,\r\nthe\r\nquestion\r\ncould\r\npertain to\r\nsome fact\r\nabout\r\nyourself\r\nthat youâ€™d\r\nprefer to\r\nkeep to\r\nyourself:\r\nâ€œWhy\r\naren''t you\r\ndrinking\r\ntonight?"\r\nYou''re on\r\nthe wagon,\r\nand you\r\nfeel it''s\r\nno one\r\nbusiness\r\nas to\r\nwhy.<br>\r\n\r\n<br><br>\r\n<a\r\nhref="http://www.fab8thproductions.com/pictures/nnn.jpg"\r\ntarget="_blank">\r\n<img\r\nsrc="http://www.fab8thproductions.com/pictures/nnn.jpg"\r\nwidth="80%" height="280"/>\r\n</a>\r\n<br><br>\r\n\r\n\r\nThe\r\nquestions\r\nwe\r\nconsider\r\ntoo\r\npersonal\r\ndonâ€™t, of\r\ncourse,\r\nneed to\r\ncome from\r\nstrangers.\r\nSometimes\r\nthey come\r\nfrom\r\nfriends or\r\nco-workers\r\nwho find\r\nsomething\r\nout about\r\nyou that\r\nthey\r\ndidnâ€™t\r\nknow\r\nbefore,\r\nsuch as\r\nthe fact\r\nthat you\r\ntook 5\r\nyears to\r\ncomplete\r\nhigh\r\nschool.\r\nThe reason\r\nmight have\r\nbeen\r\nsomething\r\nvery\r\npersonal,\r\nand you''d\r\nrather no\r\none knew.\r\nHowever,\r\nyou feel\r\nobligated\r\nto provide\r\nan\r\nexplanation because\r\nthe\r\nquestioner\r\nseems\r\ngenuinely\r\ninterested\r\nin getting\r\nan answer.\r\n\r\nOne common\r\ntendency\r\nthat\r\npeople\r\nhave in\r\nthese\r\nsituations\r\nis to make\r\nsomething\r\nup thatâ€™s\r\nnot quite\r\ntrue. You\r\ncome up a\r\nstory that\r\nseems to\r\nsatisfy\r\nthe\r\nquestioner, and\r\nthe\r\nconversation\r\nmoves on\r\nfrom\r\nthere. The\r\nproblem\r\nwith this\r\nstrategy\r\nis that it\r\ncan turn\r\nout to\r\nhaunt you\r\nlater when\r\nthe facts\r\ncome out.\r\nIf it\r\nremains\r\nlodged in\r\nyour\r\nconversation\r\npartnerâ€™s\r\nmemory,\r\nyou''ll\r\nhave no\r\nchoice but\r\nto keep up\r\nthe\r\npretense\r\nfrom then\r\non out.\r\n<br>\r\n\r\n<br><br>\r\n<a\r\nhref="http://www.fab8thproductions.com/pictures/nnnn.jpg"\r\ntarget="_blank">\r\n<img\r\nsrc="http://www.fab8thproductions.com/pictures/nnnn.jpg"\r\nwidth="80%" height="280"/>\r\n</a>\r\n<br><br>\r\n\r\n<br><br>\r\n<a\r\nhref="http://www.fab8thproductions.com/pictures/nnnnn.jpg"\r\ntarget="_blank">\r\n<img\r\nsrc="http://www.fab8thproductions.com/pictures/nnnnn.jpg"\r\nwidth="80%" height="280"/>\r\n</a>\r\n<br><br>\r\n\r\n\r\nAnother\r\npossible\r\nscenario\r\noccurs\r\nwhen\r\nyouâ€™re in\r\na\r\nconversation\r\nwith a\r\nperson\r\nperforming\r\na service\r\non you\r\nsuch as\r\ngetting\r\nyour hair\r\nstyled or\r\ngoing to\r\nthe\r\ndentist.\r\nDepending\r\non the\r\nlength of\r\ntime the\r\nprocedure\r\ntakes and\r\nhow able\r\nyou are to\r\nmaintain\r\nyour end\r\nof the\r\nconversation,\r\nthereâ€™s a\r\nchance\r\nthat the\r\nperson\r\ntaking\r\ncare of\r\nyou starts\r\nto venture\r\ninto\r\nterritory\r\nthat you\r\nfeel is\r\noverly\r\npersonal.\r\nYouâ€™re\r\nunable to\r\nmove away,\r\nas you\r\nwould be\r\nat a party\r\nor in an\r\noffice\r\nhallway,\r\nand faced\r\nwith an\r\nonslaught\r\nof probing\r\nquestions\r\nall you\r\ncan do is\r\nsquirm or\r\nfeign\r\nsleep\r\n(link is\r\nexternal).<br>\r\n\r\n<br><br>\r\n<a\r\nhref="http://www.fab8thproductions.com/pictures/nnnnnnn.jpg"\r\ntarget="_blank">\r\n<img\r\nsrc="http://www.fab8thproductions.com/pictures/nnnnnnn.jpg"\r\nwidth="80%" height="280"/>\r\n</a>\r\n<br><br>\r\n\r\n\r\nNosiness\r\nis not a\r\nproblem\r\ngenerally\r\nstudied by\r\npsychologists,\r\ndespite\r\nthe quip\r\nthat\r\npeople\r\noften make\r\nabout the\r\nreason we\r\nget into\r\nthis\r\nprofession\r\nin the\r\nfirst\r\nplace\r\n(i.e.\r\nbecause\r\nweâ€™re the\r\nones who\r\nare nosy).\r\n<br>\r\n\r\nAccording\r\nto\r\nfab8thproductions.com,\r\nit was\r\nfound to\r\nbe a \r\ntopic of\r\nyear 2007\r\narticle by\r\nUniversity\r\nof British\r\nColumbia\r\npsychologists\r\nJason\r\nFaulkner\r\nand Mark\r\nSchaller.\r\nPublished\r\nin the\r\njournal\r\nEvolution\r\nand Human\r\nBehavior,\r\nit took up\r\nthe\r\nquestion\r\nfrom the\r\nperspective of\r\nhow\r\nknowing\r\nabout\r\nthose we\r\nmate with\r\nwould\r\nbenefit\r\nthe\r\nspecies.<br>\r\n\r\n<br><br>\r\n<a\r\nhref="http://www.fab8thproductions.com/pictures/n.jpg"\r\ntarget="_blank">\r\n<img\r\nsrc="http://www.fab8thproductions.com/pictures/n.jpg"\r\nwidth="80%" height="280"/>\r\n</a>\r\n<br><br>\r\n\r\n\r\nSee what\r\nyou think\r\nabout\r\nthese 9\r\nways\r\nfab8th\r\nsuggests\r\nin\r\nhandling\r\nthe\r\nunpleasant\r\nquestions\r\nthat\r\ninvade\r\nyour\r\nboundaries\r\nof\r\npropriety:\r\n<br>\r\n\r\n\r\n1. Be\r\naware of\r\nthe cues\r\nthat\r\nsignal\r\nnosiness\r\nahead. If\r\nyou fear\r\nthat the\r\nperson you\r\nend up\r\nsitting\r\nnext to in\r\na bus,\r\nairplane,\r\nor waiting\r\nroom is\r\ngoing to\r\nstart\r\nprying,\r\narrange\r\nthe\r\nsituation\r\nso that\r\nyou donâ€™t\r\nhave to\r\nget\r\ndragged\r\nfurther\r\ninto\r\nconversation.\r\nThis can\r\nmean\r\npulling\r\nout\r\nsomething\r\nto read or\r\nstarting\r\nto fiddle\r\nwith your\r\nphone. Or\r\nif that\r\ndoesnâ€™t\r\nwork,\r\nanswer a\r\nfew\r\nquestions\r\npolitely\r\nand then\r\nshift your\r\nattentional focus\r\nelsewhere.<br>\r\n\r\n\r\n2. Tell\r\nthe truth.\r\nAs I\r\npointed\r\nout\r\nearlier,\r\nonce you\r\nstart to\r\nlie you\r\nmay find\r\nyourself\r\ninextricably\r\nbound to\r\nfacts that\r\nlater\r\nconversations\r\ncanâ€™t\r\nsupport.\r\nYou donâ€™t\r\nhave to\r\ngive all\r\nthe facts,\r\nbut the\r\nones you\r\nrelate\r\nshould be\r\nfact not\r\nfiction.<br>\r\n\r\n\r\n3. Decide\r\nwhat makes\r\nthe\r\nquestion\r\nâ€œnosy.â€\r\nItâ€™s\r\npossible\r\nthe\r\nquestioner\r\nhas no ill\r\nwill in\r\nmind but\r\nis just\r\nasking an\r\nordinary\r\nquestion.\r\nYou, on\r\nthe other\r\nhand, may\r\nfeel itâ€™s\r\nnosy\r\nbecause it\r\nbumps up\r\nagainst a\r\nfact in\r\nyour life\r\nthat\r\nyouâ€™re\r\nsensitive\r\nto (such\r\nas the\r\nmatter of\r\nyour high\r\nschool\r\neducation). If\r\nitâ€™s truly\r\nan issue\r\nof\r\nsensitivity,\r\nthe fact\r\nthat you\r\nfeel\r\ninvaded\r\nmay help\r\nyou\r\nunderstand\r\nsome of\r\nyour own\r\npersonal\r\ninsecurities\r\nand\r\nconcerns.\r\n<br>\r\n\r\n4. Keep\r\nthe notion\r\nof\r\ninclusive\r\nfitness in\r\nmind. If\r\nitâ€™s true\r\nthat the\r\nsurvival\r\nof our\r\nfamilies\r\nare\r\nforemost\r\nin our\r\nmind, itâ€™s\r\npossible\r\nthat\r\nrelatives\r\nmay ask\r\nyou\r\nquestions\r\nnot\r\nbecause\r\nthey care\r\nabout you\r\nbut\r\nbecause\r\nthey care\r\nabout\r\nthemselves. The\r\nsearch for\r\ninformation on\r\nyour\r\nlikelihood\r\nof having\r\nchildren\r\nmay simply\r\nfit into\r\nthis\r\nevolutionary\r\nframework\r\nand not be\r\none that\r\nreflects\r\nany of\r\nyour own\r\nshortcomings.\r\n <br>\r\n\r\n\r\n5.\r\nPractice a\r\nsocially\r\nacceptable\r\nway to\r\nrespond to\r\ncommon\r\nquestions.\r\nIf you\r\nkeep\r\ngetting\r\nthe same\r\nquestions\r\nover and\r\nover\r\nagain,\r\nsuch as\r\nhaving to\r\nexplain\r\nwhy you\r\nand the\r\nrest of\r\nyour\r\nfamily\r\nhave\r\ndifferent\r\nlast\r\nnames,\r\nfigure out\r\nan answer\r\nthat you\r\ncan use\r\nwithout\r\nfeeling\r\nthat you\r\nneed to\r\nexplain\r\nanything\r\nabout your\r\nrelationship\r\npast. \r\n<br>\r\n\r\n\r\n6. Use\r\ndeflection. Rather\r\nthan\r\ndeception,\r\nuse\r\ndeflection\r\nto change\r\nthe\r\nsubject\r\nwhen\r\nthings get\r\ntoo\r\npersonal.\r\nThe\r\nquestioner\r\nmay not be\r\nhappy\r\nabout\r\nthis, but\r\nif you\r\nfeel that\r\nsomeone is\r\ntreading\r\ntoo much\r\non your\r\npersonal\r\nturf, pull\r\nout and\r\nshift the\r\nfocus. If\r\nyouâ€™re at\r\na social\r\ngathering,\r\nyou can\r\nalways\r\nfind a way\r\nto move on\r\nto someone\r\nelse (â€œI\r\nneed to\r\nrefill my\r\nplateâ€) or\r\nengage\r\nsomeone\r\nnearby in\r\nconversation\r\nand then\r\nquietly\r\ndisappear.\r\n<br>\r\n\r\n\r\n7. State\r\nyour\r\ndiscomfort. It\r\nmay not\r\nseem\r\nsocially\r\nacceptable\r\nto let\r\nsomeone\r\nknow\r\nyouâ€™re\r\nfeeling\r\ninvaded\r\nbut, by\r\nmaking\r\nyour\r\ndesires\r\nknown to\r\nthe other\r\nperson,\r\nyouâ€™re\r\nactually\r\ndoing both\r\nof you a\r\nfavor. \r\nBecause\r\npeople\r\ndonâ€™t\r\nalways\r\nrealize\r\nthat an\r\nâ€œinnocentâ€\r\nquestion\r\nactually\r\nis too\r\npersonal,\r\nmost will\r\nrespect\r\nyour\r\ndesire for\r\ndistance\r\nand\r\nappreciate\r\nyour\r\nhonesty in\r\ncommunicating\r\nthis. <br>\r\n\r\n\r\n8. Realize\r\nthat some\r\npeople are\r\nâ€œcompulsive communicators.â€\r\nThere are\r\nsome\r\nindividuals who\r\njust canâ€™t\r\nstop\r\ntalking.\r\nAs\r\ndescribed\r\nin a 2015\r\npaper by\r\nOakland\r\nUniversityâ€™s\r\nRobert\r\nSidelinger\r\nand Angelo\r\nStateâ€™s\r\nDerek\r\nBolen,\r\nitâ€™s not\r\nonly that\r\nsome\r\nstudents\r\ncanâ€™t stop\r\ntalking in\r\nclass, but\r\nthat some\r\ninstructors donâ€™t\r\nknow when\r\nto give\r\nthose\r\nstudents a\r\nchance to\r\nparticipate.\r\nSome of\r\nthose hair\r\nstylists\r\nand dental\r\nassistants\r\nask\r\nquestion\r\nafter\r\nquestion\r\nabout\r\ntheir\r\nclients or\r\npatients\r\nbecause\r\nthey donâ€™t\r\nknow any\r\nother way\r\nto\r\ninteract.\r\nThereâ€™s no\r\nreason you\r\nhave to be\r\nforced to\r\nlisten to\r\ntheir\r\npatter,\r\nespecially\r\nwhen it\r\nbecomes\r\nburdensome\r\nto you.\r\nThrough\r\nyour\r\nnonverbal\r\ncues, you\r\ncan let\r\nthem know\r\nthat youâ€™d\r\nprefer a\r\nlittle\r\npeace and\r\nquiet.\r\n<br>\r\n\r\n\r\n9. Donâ€™t\r\nbe too\r\nnosy\r\nyourself.\r\nWe more\r\neasily\r\nrecognize\r\nthe\r\nfailings\r\nof others\r\nthan we\r\nare able\r\nto see the\r\nsame ones\r\nin\r\nourselves.\r\nItâ€™s\r\npossible\r\nthat your\r\nconversation\r\npartner is\r\nsimply\r\nreciprocating\r\nto the\r\ncues\r\nyouâ€™ve\r\nprovided\r\nby your\r\nown\r\nquestions.\r\nStop and\r\nask\r\nyourself\r\nwhether\r\nyouâ€™ve\r\npried a\r\nlittle bit\r\ntoo much\r\nin the\r\npast, and\r\nif so, by\r\ndialing it\r\ndown at\r\nyour end\r\nyouâ€™ll\r\nhelp\r\nmaintain\r\nconversational\r\nboundaries. <br>\r\n\r\n\r\nNosy\r\npeople are\r\na definite\r\nnuisance\r\nin life,\r\nbut with\r\nthese\r\nfab8th\r\nnine tips,\r\nyouâ€™ll be\r\nable to\r\nminimize\r\nthe\r\nintrusive\r\ndamage\r\nthey can\r\ninflict.\r\nYou can\r\nalso learn\r\nfrom the\r\nfacts in\r\nyour own\r\nlife that\r\nyou prefer\r\nto hide\r\nboth to\r\nothers,\r\nand\r\nperhaps\r\neven\r\nyourself. \r\n\r\n<br>  \r\n\r\nSo tell us\r\npeeps by\r\ncommenting\r\nbelow <br>\r\nWhat do\r\nyou think\r\nabout our\r\nfabulous\r\nnine tips\r\nin\r\nhandling\r\nnosy\r\npeople?\r\n\r\n\r\n', '24-Jun-2015', '11:58 PM', 17);
